      <h4 class="title__question">
        <span class="faq__abbreviation">Q:</span>What do you do with my donated items?
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="faq__answer">
      <span class="faq__abbreviation">A:</span>I am available to take the heavy lifting out of donation drop offs and consignments for an additional hourly charge. I am a supporter of the Northside Neighborhood House (​https://www.nnhouse.org/​ ) and usually do donations there and will provide you with your tax donation form. I have great relationships with several consignment outlets and we can together determine the best source for your gently used items.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="article__faq">
