    <p class="faq__answer">
      <span class="faq__abbreviation">A:</span>I require a non refundable deposit of half the price of quoted services at the time of booking, made via credit card. All additional payments can be made by cash, check, or credit card.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="article__faq">
